Task-2

You visit the Facebook page of the target company, hoping to get some of their employee names. What kind of reconnaissance activity 
is this? (A for active, P for passive)
> P
You ping the IP address of the company webserver to check if ICMP traffic is blocked. What kind of reconnaissance activity is this?
> A
You happen to meet the IT administrator of the target company at a party. You try to use social engineering to get more information 
about their systems and network infrastructure. What kind of reconnaissance activity is this?
> A

